<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Plastic Resin | Tangram Electronics</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
  --mint:        #e8f8f5;
  --light-teal:  #c8f2ec;
  --soft-teal:   #b2ece3;
  --teal-brand:  #2ecfb0;
  --teal-deep:   #0a9e84;
  --teal-dark:   #077d68;
  --grad-start:  #0d5c52;
  --grad-mid:    #0e7a68;
  --grad-end:    #1a9e85;
  --text-head:   #0d1f1b;
  --text-muted:  rgba(13,31,27,0.62);
}

html { 
  scroll-behavior: smooth; 
}

body {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  background: #ffffff;
  color: var(--text-head);
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 120px 48px 80px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 80% 30%, rgba(46,207,176,.18) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 10% 80%, rgba(10,158,132,.13) 0%, transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* decorative ring */
    .hero-ring {
      position: absolute; right: 60px; top: 180px;
      width: 320px; height: 320px; border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px dashed rgba(46,207,176,.25);
      animation: spin 28s linear infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    /* ─── TWO-COLUMN HERO INNER ─── */
    .hero-inner {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-text { max-width: 580px; }

    /* ─── HERO IMAGE RIGHT ─── */
    .hero-image-wrap {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      animation: fadeUp .85s .35s ease both;
    }
    /* decorative blob behind image */
    .hero-image-wrap::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      width: 90%;
      height: 90%;
      border-radius: 40% 60% 55% 45% / 50% 45% 55% 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light-teal) 0%, var(--soft-teal) 100%);
      opacity: .65;
      z-index: 0;
      animation: blobMorph 9s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes blobMorph {
      0%   { border-radius: 40% 60% 55% 45% / 50% 45% 55% 50%; }
      50%  { border-radius: 55% 45% 40% 60% / 45% 55% 50% 50%; }
      100% { border-radius: 48% 52% 62% 38% / 52% 40% 60% 48%; }
    }
    .hero-image-wrap img {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 480px;
      height: 420px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(10,158,132,.22), 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.8);
      transition: transform .4s ease, box-shadow .4s ease;
    }
    .hero-image-wrap img:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.01);
      box-shadow: 0 32px 72px rgba(10,158,132,.28), 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
    }
    /* floating badge on image */
    .img-badge {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -14px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad-start), var(--teal-brand));
      color: #fff;
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 8px 22px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      z-index: 2;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(10,158,132,.35);
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: var(--teal-deep);
      color: #fff; border-radius: 40px;
      padding: 6px 18px; font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .8px; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeUp .7s ease both;
    }
    .hero-badge::before {
      content: ''; display: block;
      width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--teal-brand);
      animation: pulse 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%,100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50%      { opacity: .4; transform: scale(.7); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(22px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5.5vw, 4.2rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--text-head);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      animation: fadeUp .75s .1s ease both;
    }
    h1 em { color: var(--teal-deep); font-style: italic; }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 540px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      animation: fadeUp .75s .2s ease both;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeUp .75s .3s ease both;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad-start), var(--grad-end));
      color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 50px;
      padding: 14px 36px; font-size: .95rem;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer; letter-spacing: .2px;
      transition: transform .18s, box-shadow .18s;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(10,158,132,.3);
      text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(10,158,132,.38); }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--teal-deep);
      border: 2px solid var(--teal-deep);
      border-radius: 50px;
      padding: 13px 34px; font-size: .95rem;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer; letter-spacing: .2px;
      transition: background .2s, color .2s;
      text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--teal-deep); color: #fff; }

    /* ─── STAT STRIP ─── */
    .stats-strip {
      display: flex; gap: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad-start) 0%, var(--grad-mid) 60%, var(--grad-end) 100%);
      padding: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .stat-item {
      flex: 1; text-align: center;
      padding: 36px 20px;
      position: relative;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    }
    .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem; color: #fff;
      display: block; line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: .8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ─── SECTION COMMONS ─── */
    section { padding: 96px 48px; }
    .section-tag {
      font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: var(--teal-deep); margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.15; color: var(--text-head);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .section-intro {
      font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    /* ─── RESIN GRID ─── */
    .resins-section { background: var(--mint); }
    .resins-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .resin-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 28px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--light-teal);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform .22s, box-shadow .22s;
      cursor: default;
    }
    .resin-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(10,158,132,.13);
      border-color: var(--teal-brand);
    }
    .resin-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grad-start), var(--teal-brand));
      transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform .28s ease;
    }
    .resin-card:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
    .resin-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 14px;
      background: var(--light-teal);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
    .resin-name {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text-head);
    }
    .resin-full {
      font-size: .82rem; color: var(--teal-deep);
      font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: .3px;
    }
    .resin-desc {
      font-size: .88rem; color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ─── INDUSTRIES ─── */
    .industries-section {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--light-teal) 0%, var(--mint) 100%);
    }
    .industries-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .ind-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--soft-teal);
      text-align: center;
      transition: background .2s, transform .2s;
    }
    .ind-card:hover { background: #fff; transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .ind-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
    .ind-label { font-weight: 600; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--text-head); }

    /* ─── PROCESSES ─── */
    .process-section { background: var(--mint); }
    .process-list {
      display: flex; gap: 0; position: relative;
      margin-top: 48px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .process-list::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: 36px; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal-brand), var(--teal-deep));
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .process-step {
      flex: 1; min-width: 160px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      text-align: center; padding: 0 16px;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
    }
    .step-dot {
      width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad-start), var(--teal-brand));
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(10,158,132,.3);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .step-label {
      font-weight: 600; font-size: .92rem;
      color: var(--text-head); margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .step-sub { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ─── WHY CHOOSE ─── */
    .why-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--grad-start) 0%, var(--grad-mid) 60%, var(--grad-end) 100%);
      padding: 96px 48px;
    }
    .why-section h2, .why-section .section-tag { color: #fff; }
    .why-section .section-intro { color: rgba(255,255,255,.72); }
    .why-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px; margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .why-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      border-radius: 20px; padding: 36px 28px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      transition: background .22s, transform .22s;
    }
    .why-card:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.17);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .why-icon {
      width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .why-title {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.18rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .why-desc { font-size: .87rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.72); line-height: 1.68; }

    /* ─── CONTACT ─── */
    .contact-section { background: var(--mint); }
    .contact-wrap {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px; align-items: center;
    }
    .contact-info h2 { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .contact-info p {
      font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .contact-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
    .contact-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    }
    .contact-dot {
      width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 12px;
      background: var(--light-teal);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0;
      color: var(--teal-deep);
    }
    .contact-label { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .8px; }
    .contact-val { font-size: .97rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-head); margin-top: 2px; }
    .contact-val a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .contact-val a:hover { color: var(--teal-deep); }

    .contact-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 48px 40px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--soft-teal);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(10,158,132,.08);
    }
    .contact-card h3 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .contact-card p { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .form-group label {
      display: block; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-head); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: .3px;
    }
    .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--soft-teal);
      border-radius: 12px; font-size: .9rem;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--mint); color: var(--text-head);
      transition: border-color .18s;
      outline: none; resize: vertical;
    }
    .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus, .form-group textarea:focus {
      border-color: var(--teal-deep);
    }
    .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer {
      background: var(--grad-start);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.75);
      padding: 40px 48px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px;
    }
    footer .foot-logo {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem; color: #fff;
    }
    footer .foot-logo span { color: var(--teal-brand); }
    footer p { font-size: .82rem; }
    footer a { color: var(--teal-brand); text-decoration: none; }

    /* ─── SCROLL REVEAL ─── */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px);
      transition: opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease;
    }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .hero-inner {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 48px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-text { max-width: 100%; }
      .hero-sub { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
      .hero-actions { justify-content: center; }
      .hero-image-wrap img { max-width: 380px; height: 300px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      section { padding: 72px 24px; }
      .hero { padding: 110px 24px 72px; }
      .hero-ring { width: 180px; height: 180px; right: 20px; top: 140px; }
      .stats-strip { flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .stat-item { flex: 1 0 50%; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); }
      .contact-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .process-list::before { display: none; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn-primary, .btn-outline { text-align: center; }
      .hero-image-wrap img { height: 240px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-ring"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">

    <!-- LEFT: Text Content -->
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-badge">Plastic Resin Supplier · BD-Wide Delivery</div>
      <h1>High-Quality <em>Plastic Resin</em> at Competitive Prices</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Tangram offers premium PP, PS, PVC, ABS &amp; engineering resins sourced from certified manufacturers — with fast delivery and expert support across Bangladesh.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="#contact">Request a Quote</a>
        <a class="btn-outline" href="#resins">View Our Resins</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Product Image -->
    <div class="hero-image-wrap">
      <img
        src="https://tangramelectronics.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Image_20260114153354.jpg"
        alt="Tangram Plastic Resin Products"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <div class="img-badge">Premium Quality Resins</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS STRIP -->
<div class="stats-strip">
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">10+</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Resin Types</span>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">BD-Wide</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Fast Delivery</span>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">100%</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Quality Certified</span>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-item">
    <span class="stat-num">24/7</span>
    <span class="stat-label">Expert Support</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- RESIN RANGE -->
<section class="resins-section" id="resins">
  <div class="section-tag reveal">Our Product Range</div>
  <h2 class="reveal">Premium Resins for<br>Every Application</h2>
  <p class="section-intro reveal">All materials are sourced from certified manufacturers and undergo strict quality checks to ensure performance, consistency, and reliability.</p>

  <div class="resins-grid">
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">🔵</div>
      <div class="resin-name">PP</div>
      <div class="resin-full">Polypropylene</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">Versatile, lightweight thermoplastic ideal for packaging, automotive parts, and consumer goods requiring high chemical resistance.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">🟢</div>
      <div class="resin-name">LDPE</div>
      <div class="resin-full">Low-Density Polyethylene</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">Flexible and durable — commonly used in films, bags, and squeeze bottles with excellent moisture resistance.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">🟩</div>
      <div class="resin-name">HDPE</div>
      <div class="resin-full">High-Density Polyethylene</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">Rigid and strong, suited for containers, pipes, and industrial applications needing high tensile strength.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">🔶</div>
      <div class="resin-name">LLDPE</div>
      <div class="resin-full">Linear Low-Density Polyethylene</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">Exceptional puncture and tear resistance — widely used in stretch films, liners, and flexible packaging.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">⚪</div>
      <div class="resin-name">PS</div>
      <div class="resin-full">Polystyrene</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">Rigid, clear material perfect for disposable cutlery, CD cases, lab ware, and insulation foam applications.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">🔴</div>
      <div class="resin-name">ABS</div>
      <div class="resin-full">Acrylonitrile Butadiene Styrene</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">Tough engineering plastic with excellent surface finish, used in automotive parts, electronics housings, and toys.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">🟤</div>
      <div class="resin-name">PVC</div>
      <div class="resin-full">Polyvinyl Chloride</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">Highly versatile in rigid and flexible forms — used in pipes, wire insulation, flooring, and medical tubing.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="resin-card reveal">
      <div class="resin-icon">💎</div>
      <div class="resin-name">PC</div>
      <div class="resin-full">Polycarbonate &amp; Engineering Plastics</div>
      <div class="resin-desc">High-performance engineering resins offering optical clarity, heat resistance, and superior impact toughness.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INDUSTRIES -->
<section class="industries-section">
  <div class="section-tag reveal">Industries Served</div>
  <h2 class="reveal">Powering Diverse<br>Industries</h2>
  <p class="section-intro reveal">Our resins are trusted by manufacturers across Bangladesh's most demanding sectors.</p>
